Kenyan parliament pass a bill for 11 controversial laws to be
"repealed or amended where deemed necessary" before the coming
General Elections and to set up a commission to review Kenya's
constitution.
</P>
<P>
Observers here noted that as events in the Opposition camp
unfold, whether the meeting between Moi and Opposition leaders
will take off at due time remains to be seen. 
