<HEADLINE> Vice President Encourages Girls to Reach for Stars </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, July 18 (Xinhua) -- U.S. Vice President Al Gore on
Friday encouraged a group of teen-age girls to reach for the
stars, while unveiling a photograph of Mars taken by the Mars
Pathfinder.
</P>
<P>
Standing next to a model of the Pathfinder's Sojourner rover,
Gore told about 100 members of the leadership organization Girls
Nation "I want you to dream."
</P>
