autonomous region and is an example of the success of the CPC's
attempt to settle ethnic problems, and provided an example of
regional ethnic autonomy for the rest of China, said Buhe.
</P>
<P>
The Party committee and government of the Autonomous Region
have placed great importance on ethnic unity and progress for the
past 50 years. Since 1983, the region has held five such
commendation conferences, promoting ethnic unity and progress in
the region.
</P>
<P>
The region has witnessed economic development, ethnic unity,
social stability, and a sound border defense, Buhe pointed out by
saying that this demonstrates the success and vitality of the
regional ethnic autonomy system.  
