trainer aircraft Friday from France, which will enable it to
restart pilot training after three years' disruption.
</P>
<P>
Shettima Abba-Gana, commandant of the Nigerian College
of Aviation Technology in Zaria of Kaduna State, said about 25 more
aircraft are expected to be delivered by various countries in
Europe.
</P>
<P>
