vocational education and the structuring of Co-operative and
Rural Development Bank.
</P>
<P>
Apart from the private sector, Lorentzen said, Denmark planned
to provide financial support to Tanzania's health, road transport
and agricultural improvement.
</P>
<P>
The detailed assistance to the three sectors was not
immediately known but support to the agricultural sector will be
directed to four selected regions: Dodoma, Iringa, Mbeya and
Morogoro. 
